000001*****************************************************************         
000003* PCWS159 - PRINT PACKAGE CENTRAL STOCK SML - DATA -  SOCKETS   *         
000004*                                                               *         
000005* THIS IS THE LAYOUT FOR THE DATA PORTION OF A SHIPPING LABEL.  *         
000006* IT MUST BE PRECEDED BY THE FORMS RECORDS DESCRIBED IN PCSW119.*         
000007* CONTROL FIELDS SUCH AS ' U01', ' U02' ETC HAVE A X'02' IN THE *         
000008* FIRST POSITION.                                               *         
000009*                                                               *         
000010* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *         
000011*                    I M P O R T A N T                          *         
000012* THE LABEL COMMANDS ARE STRUNG TOGETHER UNDER ONLY 4-05 LEVELS *         
000013* EACH LABEL COMMAND IS SEPARATED BY AN END OF TEXT CHAR-HEX 03 *         
000014* THIS WAS DONE TO TRY TO SPEED UP TRANSMISSION VIA NEW SOCKET  *         
000015* INTERFACE.  SYSTEC'S SOFTWARE SEPARATES 05 LEVELS INTO        *         
000016* STATEMENTS.  THE MAXIMUM LENGTH IS 240.                       *         
000020*****************************************************************         
000900                                                                          
001000 01  PC159-MAX-LABEL-LINES            PIC S9(04) VALUE  +3                
001100                                                COMP SYNC.                
001101***                                                                       
001102***    NUMBER OF 05 LEVELS ------------------------------/\               
001103***                                                                       
001104***   IMPORTANT - IF LINE LENGTHS CHANGE BE SURE TO UPDATE LENGTH         
001105***               IN PC159-SML-DATA-LENGTH.                               
001106***               ALSO IF LINES ARE ADDED BE SURE TO UPDATE               
001107***                                                                       
001110*****************************************************************         
001200 01  PC159-SML-LABEL-DATA.                                                
001300     05 FILLER.                                                           
001400* U01 - STORE NAME                                                        
001500         10  FILLER                  PIC X(04)    VALUE 'U01'.           
001700         10  PC159-SML-STR-NME       PIC X(10)    VALUE SPACES.           
001800         10  FILLER                  PIC X(01)    VALUE  ''.             
001900* U02 - STORE NUMBER                                                      
002000         10  FILLER                  PIC X(04)    VALUE 'U02'.           
002300         10  PC159-SML-STR-NBR       PIC X(04)    VALUE SPACES.           
002400         10  FILLER                  PIC X(01)    VALUE  ''.             
007700* U03 - NUMBER ABOVE BARCODE                                              
007800         10  FILLER                  PIC X(04)    VALUE 'U03'.           
008300         10  PC159-SML-BC-NBR        PIC X(25)    VALUE SPACES.           
008910         10  FILLER                  PIC X(01)    VALUE  ''.             
009000* U04 - BARCODE                                                           
009100         10  FILLER                  PIC X(04)    VALUE 'U04'.           
009500         10  FILLER                  PIC X(01)    VALUE                   
009600            'C'.                                                          
