010600         10  FILLER                  PIC X(04)    VALUE 'U05'.           
010900         10  PC159-LABEL-NUMBER.                                          
011000             15  PC159-LABEL-NUMBER-N  PIC 9(04)  VALUE ZERO.             
011100         10  FILLER                  PIC X(01)    VALUE  ''.             
