011120         10  FILLER                  PIC X(04)    VALUE 'U16'.           
011130         10  PC159-LINE-NUMBER.                                           
011140             15  PC159-LINE-NUMBER-N  PIC 9(03)   VALUE ZERO.             
011150         10  FILLER                  PIC X(01)    VALUE  ''.             
